Bahut log Template aur Deployment YAML ko same samajhte hain, lekin dono alag hain.

Deployment YAML
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: frontend
Isme sab values fix hoti hain.

Template YAML
kind: Template

parameters:

- name: NAME

objects:

- kind: Deployment
  metadata:
    name: ${NAME}
Yahan ${NAME} ek variable hai. Jab aap oc process ya oc new-app chalate hain aur NAME=frontend dete hain, tab OpenShift ${NAME} ko frontend se replace karke actual Deployment, Service, Route jaise resources banata hai.

Isliye:

Template = Blueprint (parameterized definition)
Processed Output = Actual Kubernetes/OpenShift resources

